# StudyKeet - AI-Powered Study Assistant

An intelligent study application that uses AI to help students learn more effectively through the Feynman Technique, spaced repetition (Leitner system), and interactive flashcards.

## Features

- ğŸ“š **Smart Content Processing**: Upload PDFs, paste URLs, or enter text directly
