- ğŸ“ **Automated Summarization**: Get concise summaries of complex content
- ğŸ¤ **Speech Recognition**: Record your explanations for evaluation
- âœ… **Coverage & Accuracy Grading**: AI evaluates what you know and what you missed
- ğŸƒ **Flashcard Generation**: Automatically create flashcards from study sessions
- ğŸ”„ **Leitner Spaced Repetition**: Optimized review scheduling for long-term retention
- ğŸ“Š **Progress Tracking**: Monitor your learning journey with detailed statistics

